为什么我们说武汉战局出现了反守为攻的转机？主要有3点文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进 图|《财经》视觉中心 编辑|谢丽容一、累计确诊病例：趋势现“顶”截至2月21日24:00，全国累计报告确诊新冠肺炎病例76288例。
Why do we say Wuhan is a turning point for counter-attack? & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & nbsp; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
以下为分区趋势图。
The following is the zoning trend chart.
图1趋势线已现平顶，目前大体上可以看出：国内非湖北地区累计病例将来停留在在13000例左右，湖北非武汉地区应在19000左右，武汉48000例左右。
At present, it can be seen that the cumulative number of cases in non-Hubei areas will stay around 13,000 in the future, around 19,000 in Hubei non-Wuhan area and 48,000 in Wuhan.
最主要取决于这个新冠肺炎究竟会像SARS一样不留长尾，还是会如指数函数所预示的那样拖出一条长长的尾巴（最近有专家这样认为）。
Most of all, it depends on whether the new pneumonia has a long tail, like SARS, or a long tail, as the exponential function predicts (as experts have recently argued).
这个要先等非湖北地区数据。
We'll have to wait for non-Hubei data.
这几天国家和省市层面都有一些数据调整。
There have been some data adjustments at the national, provincial and municipal levels in recent days.
小编啰嗦几句：数据或数据口径根据实践及时做一些调整可以理解。
A few words of verbose: data or data calibre in accordance with practice to do some timely adjustment can be understood.
但希望调整时对存量、流量，旧账、新账做出区分。
But hope to adjust the stock, flow, old account, new account make a distinction.
混在一起加进“当日新增”，会造成很大困惑，以致小编在做新增量分析时不得不花很多精力审慎剔除新增中属于存量调整的部分，再“推定”或“推测”出当日的实际新增病例。
To add the phrase "added to the day" would be so confusing that the new incremental analysis would have to take a lot of effort to carefully remove the new stock adjustment and "presume" or "surmise" the actual new cases on the day.
昨天湖北的调整方式很好：存量昨晚先调，增量今天正常报；而国家卫健委今天更直接采取旧账归旧账、存量归存量的办法，从而不会干扰对新增趋势的判断，不需要小编花很多时间去校对、“破案”。
Hubei yesterday's adjustment method is very good: last night, the increase in the regular report today, while the National Health Commission today more directly to the old account, stock to stock, so do not interfere with the new trend judgment, do not need to spend a lot of time proofreading, "solve the case."
这种改进，以人为本，必须给他们都点赞！二、新增病例：各地全面向好，武汉保卫战反守为攻迹象确认图2湖北以外数据调整后延续下降轨迹。
New cases: All over the place, the defense of Wuhan is on the defensive as a sign of attack. Fig. 2 Data from outside Hubei province continues to decline after adjustment.
是否会有“超级长尾”存疑。
Whether there will be "super long tail" doubt.
21日已有近2/3的省区新增病例为零。
Almost two-thirds of the new cases occurred in the provinces and districts on May 21.
图3湖北非武汉地区确诊病例批量核减又核增后，新增病例从异常下降和上升回归正常降幅，正式在两位数水平巩固。
Fig. 3 After the number of confirmed cases decreased and increased in Hubei non-Wuhan area, the number of new cases decreased from abnormal decline and increased back to normal decline, and consolidated at double-digit level.
符合我们此前预测。
In line with our previous projections.
图4关于武汉今天要多说几句。
Figure 4 Wuhan today to say a few more words.
很多网友关心判断武汉“从防守、阻击转为进攻”的数据依据是什么？1）数据显示近日武汉五个百分之百决战取得成功。
Many netizens are interested in judging Wuhan "from defense, block into attack" what is the basis of the data? 1) Data show that Wuhan recently five 100% decisive battle succeeded.
由于武汉是此次疫情中心，疫情突然大规模爆发，导致新冠肺炎筛查、隔离、救治等资源严重不足，而这又导致疫情加速扩散，因而陷入“隔离救治跟不上—疫情扩散加快—隔离救治更加跟不上”的恶性循环，全面被动。
As Wuhan was the epicentre of the outbreak, the outbreak suddenly erupted on a large scale, resulting in severe shortages of resources for screening, isolating, and treating the disease, which in turn led to an accelerated spread of the disease, leaving it in a vicious circle of "isolation is not keeping pace - the epidemic is spreading faster - and isolation is falling further behind."
所以早期形成大量应查未查、应收未收、应治未治、应隔离未隔离的“堰塞湖”。
Therefore, the early formation of a large number of uninvestigated, uncollected, should be treated, should be isolated not isolated "Yan Sehu."
随后武汉在中央指导、全国帮助下，明确提出“尽收尽治”化解“堰塞湖”，在尽力增加医院床位同时，加大隔离、排查、确诊、收治力度，从而显示新确诊病例数明显增加，从图4可见一大片峰峰相连的堰塞湖化解过程，与图2、3的形态明显不同。
Wuhan, under the guidance of the central government and with the help of the whole country, has made clear that "accepting as many as possible" to remove "quake lakes" and at the same time intensifying efforts to isolate, screen, diagnose and treat newly confirmed cases.
这种拉锯过程持续了两周左右，反应多次化解努力之艰难惨烈，我们此前曾用“艰难拉锯战”来形容。
The process lasted about two weeks, and the reaction was difficult and brutal, as we have described it before.
从图上可以进一步看出，这一次的化解应该比较彻底；2）武汉病例增速近几日连续大踏步下降终于降至1%以下，新增出院人数19日开始超过新增确诊，20日当天可以释放500多个病床床位，21日又可以释放近800个床位。
In recent days, the number of new patients discharged from the hospital has fallen to less than 1 percent. More than 500 beds can be released on the 20th day, and nearly 800 beds can be released on the 21st.
扭转了长时间病床数追不上病人数的被动局面。
Reversed the passive situation where the number of long beds does not catch up.
须知病床床位并不就是一张床，它对应着医护人员、诊疗设施等一系列核心“抗疫”医疗资源。
The bed bed is not just a bed, it corresponds to a series of core "anti-epidemic" medical resources such as medical personnel and facilities.
从湖北公布的数据可见武汉2月20日开放病床达20989个，比一周前增加5800个；暂空床位1828个，比一周前多1060个。
Figures released from Hubei Province show that on February 20th, 20,989 beds were opened in Wuhan, 5,800 more than a week ago, and 1,828 beds were vacant, 1,060 more than a week ago.
3）还有一个迹象就是连日来我们计算的湖北密切接触者追踪比（可惜没有武汉数据）不断提高，且势头强劲。
3) Another sign is that the tracking ratio of close contacts in Hubei province, which we have calculated for days (unfortunately no Wuhan data), has been rising and gaining momentum.
说明战场重心确实已可以顾及到“流调”（流行病学调查）这个切断传染链的最关键环节。
This suggests that the battlefield center of gravity does take into account the "fluidity" (epidemiological) that is the most critical link in breaking the chain of transmission.
所以，综合起来我们认为“武汉保卫战”在经过一段时间惨烈拉锯战后已从被动防守转为主动攻击，形势将逐渐向更加有利的方向发展。
Therefore, in sum, we believe that "Wuhan Defensive" has changed from passive defense to active attack after a period of fierce battle, and the situation will gradually develop in a more favorable direction.
三、确诊病例增长率：武汉终于降到1%以下图5国内非湖北地区增长率降至0.25%，湖北非武汉地区降至0.3%，武汉继续在1%以下。
The growth rate of non-Hubei areas in China has dropped to 0.25 percent, that of Hubei province in non-Wuhan has dropped to 0.3 percent, and Wuhan continues to fall below 1 percent.
四、密切接触者追踪：近期数据显示湖北（含武汉）的追踪力度强力上升，值得期待图6湖北这个指标继续爬升！近三日的滑动平均数更显示其升势强劲：追踪比从5.89上到15.87！说明湖北（含武汉）“流调”工作正成为新的战略重点之一。
Close Contacts Tracking: Recent data show that the tracking intensity of Hubei (including Wuhan) is rising strongly, and it is worth expecting the index to continue to climb! The sliding average of the past three days shows a strong rise: The tracking ratio from 5.89 to 15.87!
这是我们高度期待的。
That is what we are looking forward to.
图7湖北和非湖北地区都在继续下降，意味着可以释放更多医疗和社会人力资源投入到新的密切接触者追踪隔离上。
Fig. 7 Both Hubei and non-Hubei regions continue to decline, which means that more medical and social human resources can be released into new close contacts to track segregation.
五、疑似病例：新增减少、存量下降图8湖北（含武汉）新增疑似病例转头向下，确认武汉“五个百分之百”功成。
Figure 8 Hubei (including Wuhan) new suspected cases turned down, confirmed Wuhan "five hundred percent" success.
图9疑似病例存量非湖北地区降至三位数。
Fig. 9 The number of suspected cases decreased to three digits in non-Hubei area.
湖北明天起应开始下降。
Hubei should start to fall tomorrow.
六、在院治疗人数：湖北非湖北都在下降，推测的“湖北确诊未入院”人数稳定图10存量下降。
The number of people in hospital: Hubei non-Hubei are decreasing, the number of people diagnosed as unhospitalized in Hubei Province is stable.
我们倒推出的“湖北确诊未入院”人数稳定。
The number of people diagnosed as unhospitalized in Hubei was stable.
七、病死率持续回升，但治愈率以更快速度增长图11病死率已连续提高两周左右，这里有病死发生时间与新确诊增加不同步的因素（非湖北地区），也有救治能力和医疗资源因素（武汉）。
The mortality rate has been rising steadily, but the cure rate is increasing at a faster rate. Figure 11 The fatality rate has been rising for two weeks in a row.
图12治愈率以更快速度上升。
Fig. 12 The cure rate is increasing at a faster rate.
八、新增出院远超新增确诊图13.1新出院人数与新确诊人数图13.2武汉一举跨过“黄金交叉”点后战果继续扩大。
Figure 13.1 Number of New Discharges and New Confirmed Numbers Figure 13.2 Wuhan continued to expand after crossing the Golden Cross in one fell swoop.
全国包括武汉在内将逐日加大释放以医院病床床位为核心的医疗资源。
Wuhan and other parts of the country will step up daily release of hospital beds as the core of medical resources.
战局由防守转为全面进攻。
The situation changed from defensive to full-scale attack.
值得庆贺！小结：武汉保卫战之拉锯战取得重大转机后，继续扩大战果。
It is a cause for congratulation! After the great turning point in the battle for the defense of Wuhan, Wuhan continued to expand its achievements.
武汉以外其他地区持续向好，整体战局加速扭转。
Wuhan outside the region continued to improve, the overall situation accelerated to reverse.
中央提出在坚决打好湖北保卫战、武汉保卫战，全力做好首都疫情防控工作前提下，实行分区分级精准防控策略。
The central government has put forward the strategy of zoning and precise prevention and control under the premise of resolutely fighting the battles for the defense of Hubei and Wuhan and doing a good job in the prevention and control of the capital.
疫情防控、复工复产两不误，湖北以外地区复工复产将有望提速。
Prevention and control of the disease, the resumption of production in areas outside Hubei Province will be expected to speed up production.
